### Create a new order
POST http://localhost:8080/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "id": "order-1",
    "customer_id": "cust-1",
    "status": "pending",
    "total": 299.99,
    "payment_method": "credit_card",
    "items": [
        {
            "product_id": "prod-1",
            "product_name": "TestProduct",
            "quantity": 1,
            "unit_price": 299.99,
            "subtotal": 299.99
        }
    ]
}

### Search orders by customer ID
GET http://localhost:8080/orders/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "query": {
        "match": {
            "customer_id": "cust-1"
        }
    }
}

### Simple search across all fields
GET http://localhost:8080/orders/simple-search?q=TestProduct
